# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok the international olympic committee said friday that negotiations between taiwan and china on the torch relay route for the #### summer olympic games are at a dead end , and the torch will not be coming to taiwan .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (o / organization
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "International"
                  :op2 "Olympic"
                  :op3 "Committee"))
      :ARG1 (a / and
            :op1 (e / end-01
                  :ARG1 (n2 / negotiate-01
                        :ARG0 (c / country
                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "Taiwan"))
                        :ARG1 (c2 / country
                              :name (n4 / name
                                    :op1 "China"))
                        :ARG2 (r / route
                              :path-of (r2 / relay-01
                                    :ARG1 (t / torch))
                              :purpose (g / game
                                    :time (d / date-entity
                                          :season (s2 / summer)
                                          :mod (s3 / sport))))
                        :ARG1-of (d2 / die-01)))
            :op2 (c3 / come-01
                  :polarity -
                  :ARG1 t
                  :ARG4 c))
      :time d
      :weekday (f / friday))

                                    :value 2)

                                    :mod (t / this)))))
            :ARG2 (o2 / or
                  :op1 (a3 / act-02
                        :ARG1-of (s / single-02)
                        :time (e2 / early))
                  :op2 (ii / idea
                        :location (b / behind
                              :op1 a3)
                        :mod (a4 / at-least)))
            :degree (p4 / part
                  :ARG1-of (g / good-02)))
      :time (a5 / after
            :op1 (w2 / war
                  :quant 2
                  :mod (v / vicious))))
